headline.print_headline: Police Detain Kremlin Critic Navalny at Rally
headline.main: Police Detain Kremlin Critic Navalny at Rally

lead_paragraph: Russian opposition leader Alexei Navalny was detained by police after breaking house arrest on Tuesday to join an opposition rally in Moscow.
